---
title: Double Creamy Bacon & Basil Pesto Pasta with Baby Leaves & Parmesan
description: Let’s whip up a dinner filled with everyone’s favourites: bacon, cheese and basil pesto. Toss them through perfectly al dente
fusilli and sprinkle on sharp Parmesan to elevate this dish to superstar level. Sit back, and enjoy!
